Angular 18: 22 May 2024(Latest)- 18.0.3 =>>>> 12 June 2024;
--------------------------------------------------------------------
1. node -v
2. npm -v
3. npm install -g @angular/cli or npm install -g @angular/cli@10.0.0
4. ng --version
5. ng version
6. ng --help
7. ng new --help
8. ng new Project_Name
9. cd ProjectName
10. ng serve
-------------------------------
Command to Uninstall Angular version and install your specified angular version:-
npm uninstall -g @angular/cli
npm cache verify
npm install -g @angular/cli@14 =>> Command to change angular version.
ng version
--------------------------------
Angular 16	3 May 2023 => Currently working on Angular 16 Version.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Component with Inline style:-
-------------------------------------
ng g c register --inline-style
-------------------------------------
Component with Inline Template:-
ng g c student --inline-template
------------------------------------------------------
Component with Inline Template and Inline Style:-
ng g c country --inline-template --inline-style
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Modules => It is collection of components [Login, Register ,Forget Password], services[API Call] and pipes[Helpers].
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Command to Create Module:-
ng g m user_auth
or 
ng generate module module_Name
--------------------------------------------
Command to create Component Inside Module:-
---------------------------------------------------
ng generate component moduleName/componentName
----------------------------------------------------
import { FormsModule } from '@angular/forms';
  imports: [
    BrowserModule,
    AppRoutingModule,
    UserAuthModule,
    FormsModule  <<== When use this then add [(ngModel)]
  ]
